title: No Dog No Life
description:
Contains 8 [b]bestiality[/b] stories:

1. Gon and I, and Several Other Things
2. Moving On
3. Same Dream Same Destination
4. First Experience at 37 Degrees Celsius
5. Bath Time
6. The Contributor Under the Bridge
7-8. No Dog No Life (1-2)
9-11. Their Limit (1-3)

Sidenote:
This has no relation to No Game No Life(pub. 2012) other than similar names; this came out in 2004.
